{"id": "1391815771436486768", "channel_id": "1391815771436486768", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "我们计划在 V2.3 版本中对累计源液提取奖励活动追加以下奖励，这可能会影响到各位的卡池抽取规划，因此提前进行说明。\n\n- 累计提取 2000 源液：忘却篇随机限定唤醒体x1，忘却篇随机限定命轮x1。\n- 累计提取 4000 源液：忘却篇随机限定唤醒体x1，忘却篇随机限定命轮x1。\n- 累计提取 5000 源液：忘却篇随机限定唤醒体x1，忘却篇随机限定命轮x1。\n- 累计提取 8000 源液：忘却篇随机限定唤醒体x1，忘却篇随机限定命轮x1。\n- 累计提取 13000 源液：忘却篇任选超维限定唤醒体x1，忘却篇任选超维限定命轮x1。\n- 累计提取 16000 源液：忘却篇任选血肉限定唤醒体x1，忘却篇任选血肉限定命轮x1。\n- 累计提取 20000 源液：忘却篇任选深海限定唤醒体x1，忘却篇任选深海限定命轮x1。\n- 累计提取 25000 源液：忘却篇任选混沌限定唤醒体x1，忘却篇任选混沌限定命轮x1。\n\n在更新完成后，对于此前已经完成该活动的守密人，该活动将重新上线，并可直接领取已达成的累计提取源液任务的尚未领取的奖励。\n\nWe plan to add the following rewards to Cumulative Sliver Prime Extraction Rewards in Version V2.3. As this may impact your gacha planning, we are notifying you in advance.\n\n• Accumulate 2,000 Sliver Prime:\nRandom Faded Legacy limited Awakener ×1, Random Faded Legacy limited Destiny Wheel ×1\n\n• Accumulate 4,000 Sliver Prime:\nRandom Faded Legacy limited Awakener ×1, Random Faded Legacy limited Destiny Wheel ×1\n\n• Accumulate 5,000 Sliver Prime:\nRandom Faded Legacy limited Awakener ×1, Random Faded Legacy limited Destiny Wheel ×1\n\n• Accumulate 8,000 Sliver Prime:\nRandom Faded Legacy limited Awakener ×1, Random Faded Legacy limited Destiny Wheel ×1\n\n• Accumulate 13,000 Sliver Prime:\nSelectable Faded Legacy Ultra limited Awakener ×1, Selectable Faded Legacy Ultra limited Destiny Wheel ×1\n\n• Accumulate 16,000 Sliver Prime:\nSelectable Faded Legacy Caro limited Awakener ×1, Selectable Faded Legacy Caro limited Destiny Wheel ×1\n\n• Accumulate 20,000 Sliver Prime:\nSelectable Faded Legacy Aequor limited Awakener ×1, Selectable Faded Legacy Aequor limited Destiny Wheel ×1\n\n• Accumulate 25,000 Sliver Prime:\nSelectable Faded Legacy Chaos limited Awakener ×1, Selectable Faded Legacy Chaos limited Destiny Wheel ×1\n\nAfter the update, Keepers who previously completed the event will regain access to the event. You may immediately claim any uncollected rewards for accumulated Sliver Prime milestones already achieved.", "timestamp": "2025-07-07T16:18:58.597000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-07-07T16:44:07.574000+00:00", "pinned": true, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1391815771436486768", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：V2.3 源液提取追加奖励 Preview：V2.3 Sliver Prime Extra Bonus", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
